verbose_text: t-Butylhydroquinone, an Nrf2 activator, significantly attenuated IIR induced intestinal injury and apoptosis, with inhibition of the overexpression of the inflammatory cytokines, Bax and caspase-3 protein and partial restoration of Bcl-2 protein expression.
